s Schlüsse auf sein Leben.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aLITERARY COLLECTIONS / European / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2016z9783110485264oZDB-23-DKU40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783205204695423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783205204695.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2016  aZDB-23-DKUb2016